•Lion Monique Welson, Club President and Lion Omobolanle Olatunde, Tail Twister The Abuja Metropolitan Lions Club will on Saturday, September 21,  usher in new set of officers for the club’s 2019/2020 lionistic year.Scheduled to hold at the Top Rank Galaxy Hotels, Utako, Abuja, the officers for investiture are Lion Monique Welson, who takes oath as the Club President; Lion Anthonia Opusunju, Vice President; Lion Helen Joseph as Secretary and Lion Omobolanle Olatunde as Tail Twister, among othersTheir investiture is in recognition of their selfless activities in Lionism which is all about service to humanity.